editorialNotes.standard: Odds are you arent in the market for a new calculator app. But you should be. And weve found the perfect one: Calzy. Calzy was a 2018 Apple Design Award winner, and for good reason. The app is gorgeous on your iPhone, iPad, and Apple Watch and was built in a way that provides a seamless experience.
editorialNotes.short: Calculate with Haptic Touch and get the results in 65 languages.
